675
00:47:08,200 --> 00:47:10,400
That's why I don't want to go back to Thun anymore.

676
00:47:13,840 --> 00:47:14,600
<i>It's so strange.</i>

677
00:47:16,080 --> 00:47:18,480
<i>Even though I can't remember anything.</i>

678
00:47:19,660 --> 00:47:20,970
<i>But for someone...</i>

679
00:47:24,560 --> 00:47:25,600
<i>even though it has been 20 years...</i>

680
00:47:28,040 --> 00:47:29,850
<i>I have never forgotten her.</i>

681
00:47:31,980 --> 00:47:32,620
Thun?

682
00:47:37,880 --> 00:47:38,830
Thun, my son.

683
00:47:44,510 --> 00:47:46,440
<i>I had been dating Kwan for a while.</i>

684
00:47:47,560 --> 00:47:51,500
<i>Even though I knew that I hiding how I felt inside.</i>

685
00:47:53,400 --> 00:47:54,670
