Regarding Kwan alone,

695
00:48:50,300 --> 00:48:52,860
I don't know how I can forgive myself.

696
00:48:54,540 --> 00:48:56,120
I wronged her so much.

697
00:48:57,040 --> 00:48:59,580
I made her said because I was not clear about myself.

698
00:49:00,750 --> 00:49:02,490
And now, what I did to Thun...

699
00:49:03,280 --> 00:49:05,720
