700
00:49:07,500 --> 00:49:08,720
I really can't do that.

701
00:49:12,880 --> 00:49:14,520
<i>But, Ai'Mes...</i>

702
00:49:15,040 --> 00:49:18,540
Don't you care how Thun might feel?

703
00:49:25,870 --> 00:49:27,870
Then how should I tell Thun?

704
00:49:28,960 --> 00:49:30,080
Should I tell him...

705
00:49:30,650 --> 00:49:31,400
"Thun...

706
00:49:32,380 --> 00:49:34,360
I am your mother's ex-boyfriend."

707
00:49:35,530 --> 00:49:36,640
Like that?

708
00:49:41,770 --> 00:49:43,980
<i>Do you believe that when he told me the truth...</i>

709
00:49:44,480 --> 00:49:46,190
I wasn't mad at him or anything.

710
00:49:47,020 --> 00:49:50,410
I was glad that he had the courage to be honest with me

711
00:49:55,790 --> 00:49:57,600
But I've never forgot about him.

712
00:49:59,070 --> 00:50:00,440
Never really.

713
00:50:01,740 --> 00:50:03,130
Did Dad know about this?

714
00:50:03,850 --> 00:50:05,320
Of course he knew.

715
00:50:05,600 --> 00:50:07,320
Your dad was the one who told me...

716
00:50:07,560 --> 00:50:09,880
"You may have someone else in your heart..."

717
00:50:09,880 --> 00:50:12,250
"But I am the real one for you."

718
00:50:15,800 --> 00:50:17,690
Dad loved you so much, you know?

719
00:50:18,030 --> 00:50:19,260
I know.

720
00:50:22,910 --> 00:50:24,780
Did you ever meet him again?

721
00:50:26,270 --> 00:50:27,710
I didn't.

722
00:50:28,060 --> 00:50:29,500
